[[File:Flag of the chief of staff of armed force.svg|thumb|right|Standard of the Chief of Staff of the Italian Army]] The '''Chief of Staff of the Italian Army''' refers to the '''Chiefs''' of Staffs of the [[Royal Italian Army]] from 1882 to 1946 and the [[Italian Army]] from 1946 to the present.
